  stable for all (bug #551080)

  03 Mar 2015; Yixun Lan <dlan@gentoo.org> ffmpeg-9-r2.ebuild:
  add arm64 support, tested on A53 board

  08 Feb 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org> ffmpeg-9-r2.ebuild:
  Add a note when virtual/ffmpeg is appropriate.

*ffmpeg-0.10.3-r1 (01 Feb 2015)
